snippet.title: PC Engine Longplay [081] Kaizou Chounin Shubibinman
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played By: ScHlAuChi

The first game in the Shubibinman series!
Pretty mediocre game, i only did it to have the series complete!
As usual you will see some weird effects like invisible sprites that are caused by YTs 60 to 30fps conversion. -
